# DocMind OS — Cursor rules (Phase 1)

- Docs: `docs/DEVELOPER_PASSPORT.md` (onboarding), `docs/ARCHITECTURAL_PASSPORT.md` (architecture)
- Stack: FastAPI + Supabase + React (Vite, TypeScript)
- Backend entry: `backend/app/main.py`; run uvicorn from `backend/`
- Use `app/core/config.py` for env; never commit `.env`
- API routes under `/api/v1/`; health at `/health`
- Prefer service layer over fat route handlers
- Match existing naming and folder layout when adding features
